---
title: Chicken & Creamy Pesto Sauce with Garlicky Veggies & Mash
description: What's a quick and easy way to bring a rich, traditional flavour to a dish? Add our much-loved Nan's special seasoning! Use it to coat chicken breast, then add a creamy basil pesto sauce and mashed potato for a dish that's all kinds of yum.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/nans-chicken-creamy-pesto-sauce-83a8b004.jpg
